{"tid":1911231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 日本擬宣布全國進入緊急狀態","createTime":"2020-03-05T07:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T14:46:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":279,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"4cbcec69dba8b13d307fdeb26667d6029c55d660","tid":1911231,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:59:36.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎持續在全球爆發，為確保口罩供應，日本擬提出特別措施修正案，宣布全國進入緊急狀態應對疫情，計劃禁止囤積及網上轉售口罩，違者可被判囚5年，罰款300萬日圓（約21萬港元）。首相安倍晉三昨表示，部份人為了轉賣圖利而大量囤積口罩，政府必須盡快介入應對。<br />\n<br />\n日本札幌再多一人確診，令北海道累積個案增至83宗。內閣官房長官菅義偉指，雖然部份地區出現小規模集體感染，但專家認為現階段仍然可能抑制感染速度，會在出現突然擴大傳播的區域，加強防控措施，暗示將會就宣布緊急狀態修例。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1715889/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%AC%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B-%E5%9B%A4%E7%A9%8D%E5%8F%8A%E8%BD%89%E5%94%AE%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%8F%AF%E5%9B%9A%E4%BA%94%E5%B9%B4</code></pre>"},{"pid":"ffc91d55f32b43390bd7cd52185335d93aeedc83","tid":1911231,"uid":187957,"like":177,"dislike":2,"score":175,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"原來緊急法係用黎對抗疫情架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d254a77008a43247fdacafce823d7e066373b2","tid":1911231,"uid":21545,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陷球剷"},{"pid":"91c55c77214b966d553ca27cb13ac2c94517d0de","tid":1911231,"uid":346806,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:02:31.000Z","msg":"部份人為了轉賣圖利而大量囤積口罩<br />\n<br />\nchi na"},{"pid":"4784066f9f95d6604b634e766552ff08f087de70","tid":1911231,"uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTi